    <item>
      <title>英美资源集团大幅削减产量以削减成本，股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-08/anglo-american-plans-deep-production-cuts-to-save-cash-next-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英美资源集团(Anglo American Plc)公布了大幅减产计划，以在物流和运营陷入困境的情况下降低成本，该公司遭遇了自全球金融危机以来的最大单日跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-08/anglo-american-plans-deep-production-cuts-to-save-cash-next-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Dec 2023 07:33:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国计划补充储备和强劲的就业数据推动油价反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-8</link>
      <description><![CDATA[因美国就业报告强于预期以及补充战略石油储备的计划，油价反弹，但由于担心全球即将出现供应过剩，油价仍将出现 2018 年以来最长的单周下跌趋势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-8</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 23:49:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
